description: Try our easy to follow Baby's Poached Chicken recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Baby's Poached Chicken Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 small chicken breast fillets (trimmed of fat)

recipeInstructions.text: Place three cups of water in a deep non-stick frying pan over medium heat and bring to a simmer.
Add the chicken breasts, reduce the heat and gently simmer for 8-10 minutes.
Add the vegetables and continue cooking for 3-4 minutes.

Remove from the heat and allow the chicken and poaching liquid to cool before placing in a blender or food processor with the rice and 1/4 cup pre prepared formula. Blend to desired consistency for babyâ€™s developmental age. Makes 10 baby serves.
